title: Generate 5 short and clear employee survey questio

messages.prompt: Generate 5 short and clear employee survey questions about collaboration

results.question: What can improve collaboration in your organization?
How likely are you to recommend our collaboration practices to others?
Do you feel confident about collaboration in your team?
How satisfied are you with collaboration?
On a scale of 1-5, how would you rate collaboration?

response.question: Do you feel confident about teamwork in your team?
How likely are you to recommend our teamwork practices to others?
On a scale of 1-5, how would you rate teamwork?
What can improve teamwork in your organization?
How satisfied are you with teamwork?
